# Diagrams

<!--
This document is the "Diagrams" section of the Arch artifact.
Use Mermaid for every diagram. Every diagram gets a caption below the code
block explaining what it shows and which RE drivers (quality attributes,
constraints) it answers to.

Diagram types used here:
  - c4-context     (always)
  - c4-container   (heavy mode)
  - sequence       (one per top flow)
  - data-flow      (when data movement is non-trivial)
-->

## 1. C4 — Context

```mermaid
C4Context
  title System Context — <!-- system name -->
  Person(user, "End user", "<!-- description -->")
  System(system, "<!-- system name -->", "<!-- one line -->")
  System_Ext(ext1, "<!-- external system -->", "<!-- ... -->")
  Rel(user, system, "uses")
  Rel(system, ext1, "<!-- ... -->")
```

*Caption*: <!-- what the diagram shows, and which RE drivers it answers to -->

## 2. C4 — Container

<!-- Heavy mode only. Delete this section in light mode. -->

```mermaid
C4Container
  title Container View — <!-- system name -->
  Person(user, "End user")
  System_Boundary(sys, "<!-- system name -->") {
    Container(web, "Web UI", "<!-- framework -->", "<!-- responsibility -->")
    Container(api, "API", "<!-- framework -->", "<!-- responsibility -->")
    ContainerDb(db, "Database", "<!-- db engine -->", "<!-- data -->")
  }
  Rel(user, web, "uses", "HTTPS")
  Rel(web, api, "calls", "HTTPS/JSON")
  Rel(api, db, "reads/writes", "<!-- protocol -->")
```

*Caption*: <!-- ... -->

## 3. Sequence — <!-- flow name, e.g. "Search request" -->

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant G as API Gateway
  participant S as Search Service
  participant D as DB
  U->>G: GET /search?q=...
  G->>S: forward
  S->>D: query
  D-->>S: rows
  S-->>G: result
  G-->>U: 200 OK
```

*Caption*: <!-- which RE driver this exercises; e.g. "validates NFR-003 (p95 < 200ms)" -->

## 4. Data Flow

<!-- Include only when data movement is non-trivial. Delete otherwise. -->

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  src[<!-- source -->] --> ingest[Ingest]
  ingest --> store[(Primary Store)]
  store --> analytics[Analytics Pipeline]
  analytics --> dash[Dashboard]
```

*Caption*: <!-- ... -->
